('04bf88e7-9642-4488-92de-c198bba1f668',450923,'How developer experience can escape the spreadsheet',replace('<p><a href="https://www.cortex.io/">Cortex</a> is an internal developer portal that cuts noise and helps devs build and continuously improve software. Explore their <a href="https://docs.cortex.io/">docs</a> or see what’s happening on their <a href="https://www.cortex.io/blog">blog</a>.</p><p>Cortex is also hiring, so if you’re an engineer who wants to work on these kinds of problems, check out their <a href="https://www.cortex.io/careers">careers</a> page.</p><p>Connect with Anish on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/anishdhar/">LinkedIn</a> or <a href="https://x.com/dharosaurus?lang=en">X</a>.</p><p>Ganesh is also on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/gsdatta/">LinkedIn</a> and <a href="https://x.com/gsdatta?lang=en">X</a>.</p><p>Shoutout to <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/users/4245316/alex-chesters">Alex Chesters</a>, who earned a <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/help/badges/22/great-question">Great Question badge</a> with <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/30545518/how-to-count-occurrences-of-an-element-in-a-swift-array">How to count occurrences of an element in a Swift array?</a>. </p>\n','\n',char(10)),'https://stackoverflow.blog/podcast/','https://chrt.fm/track/G8F1AF/pdrl.fm/c28362/injector.simplecastaudio.com/6fa1d34c-502b-4abf-bd82-483804006e0b/episodes/3acc52db-c3b8-448b-8ac7-6323b338c1a8/audio/128/default.mp3?aid=rss_feed&awCollectionId=6fa1d34c-502b-4abf-bd82-483804006e0b&awEpisodeId=3acc52db-c3b8-448b-8ac7-6323b338c1a8&feed=XA_851k3',1722572400,1689,0,724,0),
